Soyun come to the place for outlaws called 'Wonderland'. Though she knew a lot about this place, but it existed only inside a book she read in her previous life on Earth. Crude and violent, smelling of blood and decay - she found a perfect place to dwell in... for broken human experiment subject like her. To dwell here until the moment Alice Liddell, the true protagonist of the story, come and a novel's story finally begin.
Soyun become White Rabbit here, completely replacing previous one by killing him heartlessly. Among crazies like King of Hearts, Mad Hatter, Twins, Cheshire and others... she is white-haired ice-hearted White Rabbit with enormous physical power, deep inside hoping to return home, back to Earth.>
